    "### Automated retry\n",
    "\n",
    "This codelab sends a lot of requests, so set up an automatic retry\n",
    "that ensures your requests are retried when per-minute quota is reached."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 5,
   "id": "0eb9f592",
   "metadata": {
    "execution": {
     "iopub.execute_input": "2025-03-31T20:27:51.219118Z",
